            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">1. File Changed</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">You save a controller, view, or model file.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all">
