            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Soli instantly recompiles the necessary bytecode in memory.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-green-500/50 transition-all">
